{
  "stem": "16930.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 281.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But a lot of other countries who need American help, both financially and technically.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And if America goes down, so does those other countries in the world go down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so we have some pretty-- some very-- hopefully there will be a turnaround so that America will remain strong.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And incidentally, America-- and I was just reading it recently-- was built on Torah philosophy, the original fathers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They were even considering using Hebrew as a language, as the national language rather than English.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they also built on the principles of the B'nai Noah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "B'nai Noah are non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But the Torah gives commandments, seven aspects of commandments and sub commandments, of what every human being in the world should do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "There are laws what every Jew should do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And then there are seven mitzvots of B-nail Noah, seven commandments, and they account the, you know, details for B'nai Noah of all humanity.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "All humanity must not rob and kill, must maintain courts of justice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And America was built on this system.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And that is perhaps the closeness we have to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "America essentially, the essence of America is still a godly country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And that's why we have to be strong, be really very strong in keeping it that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Because there are a lot of forces which are undermining America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The reason I gave an interview, I saw that book, that-- that movie, And it was the greatest movie I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And what was again, the guy who produced it?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Steven Spielberg, and I read that Steven Spielberg is doing this program-- is doing this program.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had confidence in Steven Spielberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Steven Spielberg was a big man just before doing this movie.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have done any other movie, which would be big.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
